</p>
      <p id="Par39">After gaps are identified, a subsequent method is used to assess the size of the data-free gaps at each methylation site using two adjustable cutoffs: the <inline-formula id="IEq7"><alternatives><tex-math id="M17">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
