    <p>VMH and MSRB collected and prepared DNA for the southern African sample source (manuscript in preparation), VMH and WJ generated and provided the Southern African genome validation data, LE conceived of the study, BL implemented the code and wrote the first draft. AG updated the code, prepared the GitHub and Bioconductor releases and revised the draft. HP managed Sanger and bisulfite sequencing. All authors participated in writing or revising the draft. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.</p>
